Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在橡樹葉剛剛開始變紅的秋天 我們前往格羅夫果園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And at the first blush of the oak leaves, we head to the Grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的麻煩是 從一地遷徙到另一地要歷經重重危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only trouble is there's a hundred perils between here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是個危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的光 正在消逝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our light is fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個秘銀…這是我們唯一的救贖嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this mithril... It is our only salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以整個精靈族的命運…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the fate of the entire Elven race...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都掌握在你手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-...is in your hands. -Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索隆曾經是你們人類的敵人 也是我們精靈的敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron was once your people's enemy as much as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請求您重建 努門諾爾和精靈之間的聯盟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I call on you to reforge the alliance between Númenor and Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救南方大地的人類\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To save the men of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這下邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方大地真正的國王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找掩護\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指環王：力量之戒\N第一季第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃蘭迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother? Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你受傷了嗎  -沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you hurt? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安塔摩去哪了 剛才還和我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Ontamo? Ontamo was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬著走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬著走 我不會丟下你不管的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crawl. I won't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵 在這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維藍迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵 他咽氣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他咽氣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他咽氣了… -快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's gone... -Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們救救我們吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Help! Please, help! -Soldiers! Over here! We're inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵們 那個屋頂快要塌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That roof's about to come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快清出一條路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Can't get out! -Quickly, clear a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里 這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊我的手 你不會有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take hold of my hand. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前走 別走散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go forward. Stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hurry, my Queen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往橋的方向走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go towards the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他們帶離這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙爾杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur! Isildur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老博爾格巴克去抓蝸牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Bolgerbuck went snailing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金風玉露的秋日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One autumn day so fine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他找到了百只大蝸牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He found a hundred big ones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望全都是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish that they were mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格羅夫 我覺得就是這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Grove! I think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話你三天前就已經說過了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Said that three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 他說得對 我記得這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, he's right. I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到了嗎 是柴火煙  其他毛腳肯定已經開始烘烤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you smell that? Wood smoke! The others must've started bakin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布羅斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾祖父以前 經常說起南方有些山能噴射巖漿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My great-grand used to speak of mountains to the south that could spit fire-rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說這些山會休眠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said they go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會長達數百年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在新的邪惡勢力崛起時 它們才會再次噴發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only to wake again when a new evil is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蘭地足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那位朋友 那個大家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friend up there. The big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你不覺得… -覺得什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You don't suppose... -Suppose what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他能解決這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he could fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快去啊 諾瑞 -他之前還收拾了那群狼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go on, Nori. -Yes. Like he fixed those wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在等什么  -我不知道…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Uh, I don't know... I don't know if he... -What you waitin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經為我們做了那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's done so much for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再對他提要求會顯得我們有點無禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a mite rude of us to ask more of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟他說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll ask him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擋道 小家伙們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out the way, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á keuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á envinyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Envinyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開花…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lót? na...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-開花… -他在嘀咕什么\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-Lót? na... -What's he mutterin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計就是一些 很簡單的詞 好讓大樹能聽懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likely little words, so the tree'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩道克 樹可不會說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc, trees don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些樹是會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Envinyata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開花\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lót? na!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議 居然起作用了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great-goats. It's working...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á kuita! á kuita! á kuita!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在讓大樹起死回生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's fixin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如薩道克所說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like Sadoc said he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 快回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dilly, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No! -Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖女兒們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My sweet girls! My babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞 迪莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Dilly! Dilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 諾瑞 你們沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dilly, Nori, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all right. I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們請求從這座大山獲取神圣的礦石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ask for something sacred from this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作為回報 我們也會提供一些神圣的物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so we offer something sacred in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了換取你秘銀礦的使用權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In exchange for access to your mithril mines,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈族準備 連續五個世紀為這座城市供應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Elves are prepared to furnish this city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家具 動物 谷物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with game, grain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及來自埃利阿多古老森林的木材\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and timber from the elder forests of Eriador for the next five centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個世紀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們說話算數 那這個承諾可不一般…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite a promise, if they can keep it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向來信守承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never made a promise I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經學會了幾個石語的詞匯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see you've learned a few words of stone-tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 我們為什么要相信精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, why should we trust any Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不應該相信精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是普通的精靈 我可是埃爾隆德半精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For I am no common Elf, but Elrond Half-elven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在精靈身上看到了 他們在自己身上看不到的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I see in Elves that which they cannot see in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在孤身求見…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I stand before you now, alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懇求您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you to save my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊貴的國王 請幫幫我們吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, noble King. Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和我兒子說兩句話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will speak to my son now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您準備怎么答復\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is to be your answer, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說當年奧力創造我們矮人時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is said that when Aul? created our people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用到了兩種元素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he crafted us of two elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火與石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire and rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們體內的石元素渴望永恒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rock that lives within us hungers for the eternal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗拒時間的拉扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}resisting the pull of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而火元素擁抱真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the fire embraces truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信萬物總有一天都會消耗殆盡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That all things must one day be consumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-然后化作灰塵 -父親…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-...and fade away to ash... -Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從不挖掘容易塌陷的大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not dig in earth that cannot support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從不鉆入黑暗之外的深處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Delving into depths beyond the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不會冒上被 陰影 巖石和礦場埋葬山底的風險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tempting shadow, rock, and mine to bury us all beneath the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會拿矮人們的生命冒險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not risk Dwarven lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫助精靈逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to help the Elves cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cheat death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友身處險境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friend is drowning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在伸手向我求援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}reaching for me to pull him to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就因為害怕石頭墜落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You expect me to swat his hand away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我甩開他的手坐視不管嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you're afraid of a bloody rock fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈族的命運 早在幾個紀元之前就已經被決定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fate of the Elves was decided many Ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些決定者遠比我們更具智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By minds much wiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我們更有遠見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}much farther-seeing than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如若違抗他們的意志 那我們整個王國都可能會崩塌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Defy their will, and this entire kingdom might fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至整個中洲都會如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps the entire Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但精靈族的命數已盡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But their time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟老頭子 冷漠 愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lice-bearded, uncaring, old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他說得對呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會坐視不管吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not thinking of lettin' this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有別的選擇嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過其他矮人領主 對這項提議持開放態度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said the other Dwarf-lords were open to the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們自己重新開礦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we reopen the mine ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向其他領主證明 可以有安全的方法開采秘銀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}prove to them there's a safe way to gather mithril,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許能讓你父親聽進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}perhaps they'd make him listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們可以強迫你父親出手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we could force your father's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不光是我的父親啊 迪莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's more than just my father, Disa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是我們的國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's our king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我教給孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of father would I be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王的意志可以當做耳旁風\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I teach our children the will of a king
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我還算哪門子父親啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should be counted as dross to be cast to the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不應該說他是個糟老頭子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have said he had lice in his beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也不該罵他愚蠢 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Or called him a fool. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就是討厭 你對我母親的各種諷刺批評\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I detest it when you heap slag on my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親確實是有點糟糕…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, well, in your mother's case, she actually does have lice in her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm joking. I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我不能強留你吃晚飯了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't suppose I can elbow you into staying for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得向吉爾加拉德報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gil-galad must be informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快他將不再是國王 因為林頓很快將不復存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And soon, he will no longer be a king, for there will no longer be a Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這就是道別了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So this is goodbye, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從不道別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們會說Namá… -Namári?\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-We say namá... -Namári?.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含義遠比單純的“告別”更豐富\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means more than simply "farewell."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是：“愿你向善而行”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means... "Go towards goodness."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們為什么要這樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd they do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把這里變成它們的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make this their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的魔影之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their Shadow Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就把土地奪回來 把它們趕走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we take it back, and drive them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們位置不利 也沒有增援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have neither position, nor reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These lands are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須把活著的人集結起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must rally to the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者將敵人一劍封喉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or put steel down their throats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言沒有結束 我也不允許結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me. I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在苦惱什么 這又不是你的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you so bothered about? It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進 就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep moving. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫后邊的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help those people at the back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙爾杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-女王  -她還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The Queen! -She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-女王 -她來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is she hurt? -Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她沒事吧  -我還以為我們痛失女王了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is she hurt? -Is she all right? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請騎我的馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-船長… -他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Captain... -Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是戰死了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're dead, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆迪爾 我的朋友們 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arondir. My friends. My...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母親 所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的事情 會嚴重影響思緒 我們不能胡亂猜測\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What cannot be known hollows the mind. Fill it not with guesswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we even going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾在那條山脊線上安營扎寨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Númenor set their camp upon that ridgeline,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個遠處的山峰后邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beyond that far peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該和其他幸存者都跑去了那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is where they shall hie to, along with any survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mother included.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高警惕 奧克現在白天也會出來行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And be wary. The Orcs will move in daylight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前殺過奧克 你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've killed Orcs before, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像你這個年紀的時候 根本沒有奧克這種東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was your age, there was no such thing as Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在呢 你殺過多少奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now? How many have you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很多 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Many. -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會用“很好”這樣的詞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would not use such words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黑暗的殺戮行徑稱為“很好” 會讓內心變得黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It darkens the heart, to call dark deeds "good."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗會乘虛而入在我們體內滋長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It gives place for evil to thrive inside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每場戰爭都有外在之仗和內在之仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every war is fought both without and within.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此 所有士兵都必須謹慎留意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of that, every soldier must be mindful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你我也不例外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even I. Even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算士兵了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I a soldier, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們可以把你算作士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we can make one of you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要走多遠才能到達營地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much further until we reach the encampment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了這個坡就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just beyond this rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.33,0:24:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要走多遠眼前的煙霧才能散去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much further until we're clear of this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.58,0:25:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧已經散去多遠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long have we been clear of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將近一英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nearly a mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能看清楚了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.20,0:25:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看到灰蒙蒙的一片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個繼續走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep walking, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.91,0:25:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽著我的馬 別讓任何人看出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guide my horse. No one need notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃蘭迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃蘭迪爾 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.29,0:25:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們稱這里為大綠林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call it Greenwood the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.29,0:26:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把頭低下 眼睛盯緊那片懸崖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your head down and your eye on that line of cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.87,0:26:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會在遠處找到人類的居住地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll find the big folk settlements on the far side.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話 那里的人可以幫你找到你的星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With any luck, the people there can help you find your stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只能告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause all I can tell you is,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打一千多年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoot-folk haven't seen 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的祖先生活在不知名的地方以來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since the days our ancestors lived in parts unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.37,0:26:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛腳族就沒見過他們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便對你這種大長腿而言 走這么遙遠的路也絕非易事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's a long time to wander. Even for a fellow with big legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不應該偏離路線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should've just stayed on-trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.33,0:29:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道當初看到 那顆墜落的星星時 我就該放任不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I saw that star falling, I should've just let it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-埃拉諾… -您之前提醒過我 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elanor... -You tried to tell me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在才明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個毛腳族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just a Harfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.25,0:29:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠只會是個毛腳族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.20,0:29:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去睡覺吧 諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off to bed, Nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.58,0:29:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事我們可以早上再處理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can tend to the rest in the mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去過親近的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever lost someone close?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被奧克殺害的那種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說親戚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.75,0:30:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥 芬羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother. Finrod.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.41,0:30:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.25,0:30:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.54,0:30:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫凱勒博恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celeborn was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.04,0:30:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們初識于一片花叢中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We met in a glade of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.75,0:30:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我在跳舞 他看到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was dancing and he saw me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 跳舞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.95,0:31:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候戰爭似乎還很遙遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The war seemed so very far away then.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去參戰的時候 我還責備了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he went to it, I chided him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的盔甲不合身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His armor didn't fit properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.79,0:31:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就嘲笑他像個銀蛤蜊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I called him a silver clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.87,0:31:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之后我再也沒有見過他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never saw him again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.04,0:31:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前所說的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.66,0:31:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不正確\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.25,0:31:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣也并非你的本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did not intend for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.12,0:31:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給了敵人力量 所以我有責任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave power to the enemy. So that makes me responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.29,0:31:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說 世間萬物就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some say that is the way of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信聰明的人 還會審視我們的初衷和本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I believe the wise also look upon what is in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.70,0:32:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣絕非你的本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this was not in yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.95,0:32:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把今天的重擔都攬在 自己肩上 希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not take the burden of this day upon your shoulders, Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.79,0:32:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會發現 重擔一旦扛起 想要卸下就會很難\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may find it difficult to put it down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.25,0:32:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我怎么才能做到放手呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how am I to let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上 有超越黑暗的力量在運作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are powers beyond darkness at work in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許在這樣的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps on days such as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無選擇 只能相信他們的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've little choice but to trust to their designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.66,0:32:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄我們自己的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And surrender our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.75,0:32:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家沒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My home is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.37,0:32:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里邊有什么計劃可言嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the design in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在還看不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot yet see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.08,0:33:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.62,0:33:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 你聞到了什么味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? What do you smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.79,0:34:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰燼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.87,0:34:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都沒有 只有灰燼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' but ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.83,0:34:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我們這是在浪費時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. We're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.54,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能多休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rest while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.62,0:34:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天一亮我們就出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We move at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.37,0:34:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有天亮可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What light?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一波震動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.04,0:35:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得先等巖石穩定下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to give the rocks time to resettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈大師 要高度自律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Self-discipline, master Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自律能給你帶來成功嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think that'll bring you success?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正讓我在比賽中贏了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It did in our contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.66,0:35:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意輸給我的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lost on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.66,0:36:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標從來都不是打敗你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My aim was never to defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.00,0:36:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是得到你的持續關注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to gain your ear a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.29,0:36:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這精靈撒謊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.91,0:36:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時就是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.54,0:36:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累得沒喘上氣而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.87,0:36:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.66,0:36:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得 你這精靈身上有點矮人的特質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always thought you were a mite Dwarvish for an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我覺得 你是個有精靈特征的矮人 都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are a rather Elvish Dwarf, Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.04,0:36:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林之子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Son of Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那誰…的孫子 -隨便你怎么嘲笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Grandson of... -Scoff if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.45,0:37:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人最偉大的成就 就是不負父輩的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mightiest thing a Dwarf can do is to be worthy of the name of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.54,0:37:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們確實有自己的秘密名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do have our secret names,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.20,0:37:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只供自己人使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for use only amongst ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.95,0:37:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些名字只會告訴家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we reveal them only to family.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子 父母 姐妹 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wives, parents, sisters, brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.08,0:37:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-埃爾隆德… -先別說了 都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elrond... -Save it, Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.79,0:37:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成功了再告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the far side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.66,0:37:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.54,0:39:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.45,0:39:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.54,0:39:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀比我們想象的還要多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's more than we ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都林國王 有一個… -夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-King Durin, there is a... -Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.83,0:39:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, just look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那個精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seize the Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初你母親生你的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When your mother bore you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.16,0:40:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你體內是有某種缺陷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something inside you was ill-formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼吸又干又澀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your breathing was ragged and dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸聲很微弱 很可憐 就像白堊石在刮擦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A tiny, pitiful sound, like scraping chalkstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們說你肯定熬不過第一個冬天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Folk said you'd never see your first winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.83,0:40:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親哭累了入睡之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after your mother's weeping eyes had found refuge in sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.37,0:41:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會把你抱到火光下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I held you to the firelight,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.62,0:41:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚都抬著你的下巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kept your chin up all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.66,0:41:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣似乎減輕了一點負擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seemed to ease the burden a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one night,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凝視著你乳臭未干的小臉蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gazed down on your tiny, naked face,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.58,0:41:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛從中看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I saw upon it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.87,0:41:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位老矮人國王的白色胡須\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the great gray beard of an old Dwarven-king.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.20,0:41:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像奔赴戰場的軍隊一樣強大而霸氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mighty and terrible as an army with banners.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.29,0:41:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你母親醒來時我告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when your mother woke, I told her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.54,0:41:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以后不用再哭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she need cry no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.41,0:41:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們的兒子會活著 會有移山填海般的出息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our son would live and he would move mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.87,0:42:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 我挖個小洞您就能氣成這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you expect me to move mountains, Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還指望我如何移山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you fall to pieces when I dig a single hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.41,0:42:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您嘴上說著讓我立下輝煌大業\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak of greatness for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.33,0:42:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻扼殺我的所有野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you suffocate in me any ambition,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.29,0:42:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有渴望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.33,0:42:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及任何只要不是源自于您的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any thought that does not originate in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天將降大任于斯人也\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The iron that must bear the most heavy of burdens
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.91,0:42:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必先苦其心志 勞其筋骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}must also endure the most rigorous tempering!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.33,0:42:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓盟友去送死可不是苦心志勞筋骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consigning your allies to death is not tempering.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.75,0:42:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德和我情同手足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond is as much a brother to me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是同一個母親生的親兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as if he'd been fired in my own mother's womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.16,0:42:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么敢…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.66,0:42:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒大沒小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.08,0:42:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你母親的記憶說事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Invoke your mother's memory
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.79,0:42:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此來為背叛同胞的決定狡辯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to defend your decision to betray your own kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.50,0:43:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你背叛了我們的同胞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! It's you that's betrayed our kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費我們的未來 就為了讓你自己能夠活在過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Squandering our future so you can cling to the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.37,0:43:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你褻瀆了頭頂的王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You profane the crown you wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.54,0:43:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家徽放下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.95,0:43:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正再也不是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not yours anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.91,0:44:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個秋日 他捕食蝸牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while he was a snailin' Upon that autumn day
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.62,0:44:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他任由寶寶哭泣 溪流將女兒沖走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His babe he left a-wailin' The stream took her away
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.50,0:44:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比 你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Poppy? -What are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.79,0:44:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拎個桶 你覺得我能在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fetchin' a pail, what's it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.83,0:44:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個饕餮 別吃了  這些食物我們得留著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the vittles. Stop eatin'! We have to save those.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.83,0:44:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先出去看一眼 然后我們再聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you take a look outside, and then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.29,0:44:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看看那個 哇  -我們可以把那些作物賣到市場…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that! Oh, wow! We'll go to market with that crop, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.45,0:44:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.62,0:44:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 這是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.83,0:44:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.70,0:45:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他搞定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.00,0:45:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞 你敢信嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you believe it, Nori?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.87,0:45:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些吃的足夠我們今晚大快朵頤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's enough bounty here to feast tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.29,0:45:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剩下的足夠我們撐到 遷徙到凍魚區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and still have enough left over to last to Frozen Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.29,0:45:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾娃說她要做一種 叫“蘋果香腸”的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Malva's sayin' she gonna make somethin' called apple-sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.50,0:45:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是蘋果醬 -我就是這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Applesauce. -That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.12,0:45:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.54,0:45:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 瑪爾娃 你姐姐去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Malva. Where's your sister gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.91,0:45:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來弄 里邊還有空間嗎  我們好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got it. Is there more space in there? We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.83,0:45:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沿河漂流 她大聲啼哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...floated down it So loudly she did wail
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛙魚之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The King of the Frog Fishies
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.50,0:45:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她變成了一只蝸牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turned her into a snail
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.20,0:45:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老博爾格巴克 抓住了她 如此多汁 如此香甜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Bolgerbuck he caught her So juicy and so sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.08,0:45:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說這是他的小女兒 但他忍不住想…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say his little daughter He could not help but...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.66,0:47:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.91,0:47:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走錯路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.79,0:47:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去那邊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.00,0:47:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.91,0:48:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.41,0:48:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-別碰她  -聽見沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Leave her alone! -You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.41,0:48:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-滾開  -走開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Off with you now! -Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.37,0:48:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢碰她一根毛 我就敲碎你們的腦袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You harm a hair on her foot, and I'll brain the lot of ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.95,0:49:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 好了 把手伸出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. All right. Keep your hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.20,0:49:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在把雙手合起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.83,0:49:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.41,0:49:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交給我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.04,0:49:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.12,0:50:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得回家 聽到我說的話了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going home. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.58,0:50:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我們一起回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.50,0:50:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 貝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.50,0:50:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-求你了 -它不會聽你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Please. -He won't listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.00,0:50:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不聽我們任何人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't listen to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.08,0:50:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初就不應該把那個精靈拉上船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have pulled the Elf on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.45,0:51:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海里遇到她時 我就應該把她留在海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've left her in the sea, where I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.12,0:52:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.83,0:53:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝政女王在這里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen Regent. Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.91,0:53:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備工作基本完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preparations are nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.04,0:53:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以在一小時內出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can depart within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.45,0:53:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中洲南方的人怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What of the Southlanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.62,0:53:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一支駐軍將墊后 負責護送他們前往安全的定居點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One garrison will remain behind to escort them to a safe settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.54,0:54:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便尋找我們失蹤的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And search for our missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.33,0:54:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.91,0:54:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾不允許下跪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one kneels in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.79,0:54:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里不是努門諾爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are not in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.91,0:54:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不在努門諾爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither of you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.62,0:54:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fault that is mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.58,0:54:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船只都在待命 女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our ships are waiting, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.95,0:54:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開這片大陸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us put this land behind our sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.91,0:55:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別憐憫我 精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not spend your pity on me, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.16,0:55:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留著將來可憐我們的敵人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save it for our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.04,0:55:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為敵人不知道它們已經挑起了大戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For they do not know what they have begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.12,0:55:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我 彌瑞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For I, Míriel,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.91,0:55:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔爾帕藍提爾之女 我發誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}daughter of Ar-Inzilad?n, vow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾必將回歸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Númenor will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.54,0:55:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈將時刻準備著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Elves will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.20,0:55:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 我們隨時可以出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain, we sail with the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.87,0:56:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.37,0:56:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.16,0:56:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來吧 姑娘 能拿什么就幫我拿著點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your feet now, girl. Stand up. Help me gather what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.95,0:56:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞 快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.04,0:56:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別垂頭喪氣的 一切都會好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let this splinter your spirit, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.08,0:56:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉哥 別騙她 她這么大了 能聽得出真話假話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't lie to her, Largo. She's too old for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.91,0:56:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒撒謊 一切都會變好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't lyin'. It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.37,0:56:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 白蘭地足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pity's sake, Brandyfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.25,0:56:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們哭一會兒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give us a moment to weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.12,0:56:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weepin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.87,0:56:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得我們只能哭了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that all you think we have left in us?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.45,0:56:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是毛腳族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're Harfoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.50,0:57:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會屠龍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we don't slay dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.95,0:57:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對挖寶藏也沒什么興趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not much for diggin' jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.12,0:57:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我保證有件事我們很擅長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's one thing we can do, I warrant,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.41,0:57:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比中洲的任何生物都要做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}better than any creature in all Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.75,0:57:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們彼此忠貞不渝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We stay true to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.37,0:57:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論前路如何曲折 或多么陡峭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how the path winds, or how steep it gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.16,0:57:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們敢于直面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we face it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.83,0:57:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣和意志比我們的大腳還要強大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with our hearts even bigger than our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.50,0:57:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只管繼續前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we just keep walkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.87,0:58:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞 你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori. Where are you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.50,0:58:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫助我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To help my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.87,0:58:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告他將要發生的事情 這起碼是他理應得到的幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warn him what's comin'. He deserves at least that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.95,0:58:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在要偏離路線 獨自前往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goin' off-trail? Now? Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.29,0:58:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會獨行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.75,0:58:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經拋下了許多同胞 不能把他也丟下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've left enough folk behind, we're not leavin' him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.20,0:58:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆姑娘哪兒也不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You girls aren't goin' anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.79,0:58:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須有我同去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.00,0:58:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈爾迪 你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure about this, Goldie?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.91,0:58:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走進那片樹林 可能永遠都無法活著走出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go into those woods, you might never come out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.83,0:58:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有探路者一起去 她們有可能會安全返回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They might if a trail-finder were to go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.37,0:58:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蘭地足小姑娘 幫他是對的 自始至終都是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot girl was right to help him. Was right all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.45,0:59:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得瑪爾娃密都格拉斯 太過驕傲而不敢承認\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you think Malva Meadowgrass is too proud to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.04,0:59:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩道克 那你覺得 不講情義地活著還有什么意義嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, what's the good of livin', Sadoc, if we aren't livin' good?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.91,0:59:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 瑪爾娃 哪怕就一回…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Malva, just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.20,0:59:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能承認自己不是每次都對 那可就太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, it would be grand if you weren't right all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.04,0:59:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿口糧 給我拿根拐杖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll fetch provisions and get me stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.29,0:59:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm comin' with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.12,0:59:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 反正我們終有一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter anyway, we're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.00,0:59:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 不然一整天都得待在這里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, otherwise we'll be here all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.75,0:59:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們能找到他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think we'll be able to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.75,0:59:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是個巨人啊 我們怎么會找不到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a bloody giant. How could we miss him?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.75,1:00:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信她會信守諾言嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You believe she'll keep her promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.37,1:00:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.58,1:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.79,1:00:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭已經固定 傷口已經包扎 我們可以出發了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bones have been set, wounds bound. We can travel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.79,1:00:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.79,1:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安都因河口 一個古老的努門諾爾殖民地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An old Númenórean colony by the mouth of the Anduin.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.62,1:00:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們稱之為佩拉基爾 據說那里有新鮮的水源和土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pelargir, they called it. They say there's fresh land, fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.37,1:00:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個新的開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.75,1:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去向至高王報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I will report to our High King.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.00,1:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直面獎懲 任由處置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To face whatever awaits me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.95,1:00:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的國王呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what of our king?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.58,1:00:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your king?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.75,1:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人通知你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has no one informed you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.79,1:00:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Informed me of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.25,1:00:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.37,1:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you had died.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.41,1:01:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是死了反而更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better for me if I had done.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.54,1:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天夜里 南方大地的人 在路上發現他傷成了這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Southlanders found him on the road like this yestereve.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.66,1:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口一夜之間就腐壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wound soured overnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.75,1:01:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試著在路上給他治療 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought to try and treat him on the road, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.87,1:01:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傷口需要精靈族的藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wound needs Elvish medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.16,1:01:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能騎馬嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can he ride?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.41,1:01:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓治療師盡可能多帶一些口糧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have the healers gather what provisions they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.62,1:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.33,1:01:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來命運又要讓我們“同筏”共濟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems fate has in store for us one more raft.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.58,1:01:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.37,1:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄這片土地 也不同意他們將這里燒毀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not abandon these lands and condemn them to burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.08,1:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不可以放棄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nor will you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.75,1:02:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜國王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.83,1:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜國王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.75,1:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜國王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.75,1:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜國王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.58,1:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著吧…士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it... Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.00,1:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.58,1:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜南方大地以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.29,1:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜南方大地以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the Southlands! Strength to the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.12,1:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辜負了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I failed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.95,1:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.70,1:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.45,1:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.37,1:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.83,1:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父親的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your father's.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.70,1:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他年紀大了 太多疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's grown too old, too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.54,1:04:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維過于羸弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His mind, too feeble.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.58,1:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙眼發昏看不清現實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His eyes too dim to see
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.25,1:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他把你的多少家徽扔到地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that no matter how many crests he hurls to the floor,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.95,1:04:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 這將會是你的王國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one day this will be your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.04,1:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你都林四世的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin IV's.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.12,1:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你兄弟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not your brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.91,1:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是其他矮人領主的 而是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not some other Dwarf-lord's. Yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.91,1:04:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.50,1:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們氣數耗盡之前 這座山和其他所有山都將歸我們統治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And together, we will rule this mountain and all others before our time is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.29,1:04:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀屬于我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That mithril belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.62,1:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬于你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.37,1:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 我們一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And together, one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.95,1:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同去挖掘秘銀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are going to dig.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.83,1:05:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把秘銀礦封起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seal it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.04,1:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.66,1:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉你們的太陽斗篷和頭盔吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cast off your sun-cloaks and your helms.
